Quality Assurance.

profile:
MCBM Roofing Services is not your typical roofing company. We are a family-owned and operated company, specializing in residential and commercial roof installation, replacement, and repair. Our mantra is to always exceed our customers’ expectations.
Founders Marcelo Sosa and Carolina Quagliata have a passion for providing a high level of service to their clients. With 15 years of roofing experience and 20 years in customer service between them, you are guaranteed exceptional quality workmanship and a lasting relationship built on open and honest communication.
We know how crucial the structural integrity of your roof is. It protects your family and your valuables from the elements, helps make your house more energy efficient, and adds value to your home. That is why we are committed to providing our customers with the highest quality roof construction, at a reasonable price. From the beginning of a project to its completion, we pride ourselves on our high standards, professionalism, and superior results. We deliver on our promises, and we guarantee your satisfaction.

Interested in a FREE estimate?
We are a family owned company built after 15 years of experience in the industry. We specialize in offering high quality products and services for clients in Toronto and other areas in the GTA region such as Richmond Hill, Mississauga, Brampton, Vaughan, Scarborough, Newmarket, Markham, Oakville. We are prompt, professional and reliable. Call us now to book your Free Estimate. We will book a date and time that is convenient for you and your family. We promise to offer a reasonable and competitive quote while assuring that the work will be carried out by a fully qualified crew. For questions or inquiries, please do not hesitate to contact us at (416) 824 4212 or visit us at www.milestonealuminuminc.ca 
We look forward to hearing from you!

Satisfaction and Warranty

profile: Siding, Stucco, Stone, Brick, Masonry and Fireplaces From design to installation, Stone Selex Design is a premier company with over 20 years of experience providing both residential and commercial customers with quality installation and a high level of customer satisfaction. Stone Selex Design is committed to providing full service installation for your exterior or interior stone veneer project. We also provide installation of stone veneer, stucco, brick, masonry and fireplace transformations. Design your own project with the NEW Stone Veneer Visualizer and have Stone Selex Design install it for you. The Visualizer gives you the ability to envision your project from the comfort of your computer screen. It has the power to transform a photo of your home into a professional digital rendering by adding siding, stucco and stone. Make your home the talk of the neighbourhood with stone and stucco, or stone and brick, or siding and brick, stone tile and wood siding. The possibilities of style and colour combinations are endless. A Stone Selex Design project manager will help you with each stage of your project from where to add stone, stucco, siding, brick and masonry and provide you with a quote for our installation services provided by our experienced masonry installers. If it’s a fireplace that you want to create or just simply add stone or masonry, Stone Selex Design and the visualizer can help you with this too. While you are in the planning stages of your fireplaces transformation the visualizer is a great tool to use. Look through photos for ideas and see what others are doing and then come to Stone Selex Design and ask us to install it for you. Visit us here: https://twitter.com/StoneSelex https://www.facebook.com/StoneSelexInc/

CityPro Aluminum & Contracting Inc. was founded in 2000 by two young entrepreneurs to establish and continuously improve and maintain the industry's high standards. With over 10 years in the business, we are committed to integrity and ethical standards in supplying GTA with the best aluminum-siding products and services. Our goal is to provide top-quality workmanship and excellent customer service. In order to achieve this, we use highly trained installers and the best quality aluminum out there from the best suppliers. This allows us to provide 100% warranty on our work and materials.

*****

Quality, commitment and the promise of product longevity are the core philosophies of CityPro Aluminum & Contracting. All of our installations are warranted for life, if any sort of failure does occur we will fix or replace the defect, free of charge for as long as you own the home.
We carry a $2,000,000 Liability insurance to make sure safety is our top priority. All of our workers are covered by WSIB workers compensation. If we get hurt on your property, you’re not liable in any way. Copies supplied upon request.
CityPro Aluminum & Contracting covers the entire Greater Toronto area. If you decide to move forward with us, we’ll write a detailed agreement including all the specifications we discussed. Most projects are completed within 2 to 3 weeks of the agreement. We won’t accept final payment until you are 100% satisfied.

CityPro Aluminum & Contracting Inc

profile:
George Kent first opened in 1949 and has since completed over 80,000 installations.  We offer home improvement services for  the entire Greater Toronto Area from Oshawa, to Newmarket, to Orangeville, to Burlington, including Oakville, Milton, Brampton, Woodbridge, Mississauga, Etobicoke and all of southern Ontario.  
With this many years of experience, our reputation speaks for itself.  We are the only home improvement company in the GTA that offers a lifetime warranty on the original installation for our windows and roofing.  In comparison, most box stores offer 1 year on the labour and our best competitors offer 5 years.

We specialize in:
* Windows: Enerview Window and Door Solutions, Vinylbilt, Neat Glass, Energy Star, ecoEnergy, Pella, Laminated Sound Reduction Glass
* Window Styles: Casement, Awning, Double Hung, Single Hung, Double Tilt Slider, Single Tilt Slider, Double Lift Out Slider, Single Lift Out Slider, Low Profile Fixed, High Profile Fixed, Custom Shapes, Greenhouses, Bay Windows, Bow Windows
* Doors: Steel & Fiberglass, Enclosures, Patio Doors, Garden Doors, Storm Doors, Entryguard Doors, Dorplex
* Roofing: Shingle roofing, Flat roofing, Tile roofing, lifetime roofing products
* Shingles: Camelot, Capstone, Grand Slate, Slateline, Timberline HD
* Insulation: Spray Foam, Attic, Basement, Roof, Blown Insulation, Exterior Wall Insulation, BASF, Owens Corning
* Siding: Vinyl Siding, Aluminum Siding, Gentek

profile:
Topflight Aluminum is dedicated to providing quality construction and exceptional customer service. We strive to build lifelong relationships with our customers and to exceed your expectations, in every aspect of the job, from start to finish.
We’ve helped thousands of people improve the look and quality of their homes and businesses. We are proud to serve Toronto (GTA), Etobicoke, North York, Scarborough, Vaughan, Richmond Hill, Markham, Stouffville, King City, Aurora, York Region, Mississauga, Oakville, Hamilton residents with expert craftsmanship and professionalism. We pride ourselves on being able to exceed the expectations of our customers.

•	WHY TopFlight Aluminum?

1.	Quality first, Speed second
We all like our issues to be resolved efficiently when contacting a company, but what will make you use Topflight Aluminum again and again? There is only one answer. The quality of the service!

2.	Great Customer Service
We understand that building or remodeling a home is a major investment, so for us it is important that our customers feel valued. Topflight Aluminum pays special attention to what our clients want, we remember the details no matter how insignificant and deliver quality services at all times.

3.	Top Quality Materials
Apart from good workmanship and top-grade professionals handling your building project, the best quality of materials we use will be next most important factor in determining the outcome of your building.

4.	Warranty

Building your dream house shouldn’t be a nightmare! That’s why we only use guaranteed products and materials with 30- to 50-year warranties. Additionally, all of our work comes with workmanship warranty. Whether you are replacing or repairing, Topflight Aluminum can always meet your needs!

OUR MISSION
Our goal is simple… To perform for our customers the highest level of quality construction services at fair and market competitive prices. We aim to maintain the highest levels of professionalism, integrity, honesty and fairness in our relationships with our suppliers, subcontractors, professional associates and customers.





GET A FREE QUOTE
No unexpected charges —see exactly what your home needs with a free estimate.

profile:
P.C.L. Interior & Exterior Finishes Inc. Located in the Greater Toronto Area (GTA) we are your first choice for custom Exterior home renovation design and construction. Our sought after experience and quality gives you the ultimate in value and beauty for all of your Exterior needs.

We specialize in may types of Cladding Systems., such as James Hardie fiber cement products, Cape Cod, Maibec or Fraser wood siding products, NewTechWood - Wood Composites, Custom wood soffit & fascia, custom exterior moldings, eco friendly decks and walls, aluminum soffit, fascia and eavestrough, Masonry  works, exterior painting and roofing (subcontracted to licensed trades). All of our products meet or exceed the high standards that we have become known for and our repeat customers and clients reflect that.

Our professional interior home improvement services include inside remodels , custom interior trim & mouldings, design & re-designing of fire places, drywall & taping, electrical wiring & lighting (subcontracted to licensed trades), all types of flooring, and painting. We also connect our clients to designer stores for furniture, electrical and plumbing fixtures, tiles and granites. We provide direct connection with design teams for kitchens, baths and home remodeling at no expense to our clients.

Fully insured and licensed, our staff are pleased to offer free estimates and consultations to homeowners. With careful and meticulous planning P.C.L. Interior & Exterior Finishes Inc. will design, renovate and complete your custom work within your scope and budget while maintaining an exceptionally high quality of workmanship.

Our professional home design and renovation team extend their services to the GTA (Greater Toronto Area), Downtown Toronto, The Beaches and East End Toronto. We look forward to meeting with you and extend our thanks to our many satisfied customers.

profile:
At Andy Aluminum, we've been offering complete aluminum siding, eavestrough, fascia, and soffit services to customers in Toronto, ON and the GTA for almost two decades, our four man team is composed of highly trained and dedicated professionals who are able to diagnose and resolve all of your eavestrough related problems.

Your eavestrough is an integral part of your home water management system and it is crucial that it be installed and operate properly in order to avoid water damage to your home.

Installing and repairing gutters, soffit and fascia has always been and continues to be the mainstay of our company but in addition, we also offer aluminum and vinyl siding installation, window capping, aluminum flashing and leaf guards installations.

profile:
LONI Aluminum & Contracting has established itself as one of Ontario’s leading Siding, Soffit & Fascia, Windows and Doors installation, and replacement companies. We have serviced homeowners for over 20 years and we continue to provide innovative home improvement products that exceed industry standards for quality, reliability, and performance.
 
 We use highly specialized installation techniques to ensure a lifetime of satisfaction from our customers. We always strive to go beyond our customer’s requirements for beautiful, strong and thermally efficient products.
 
Quality, commitment, and the promise of product longevity are the core philosophies of LONI Aluminum & Contracting. All of our installations are warranted for life, if any sort of failure does occur we will fix or replace the defect, free of charge for as long as you own the home.
 
We carry a $2,000,000 Liability insurance to make sure safety is our top priority. All of our workers are covered by WSIB workers compensation. If we get hurt on your property, you’re not liable in any way. Copies supplied upon request.
 
When you call LONI Aluminum & Contracting, you will be greeted with a courteous, knowledgeable staff member who will be happy to assist you in any capacity. If an appointment is set we will email you a confirmation with the time and date. One of our very experienced representatives will arrive ON TIME and give you a no pressure demonstration specific to the product your interested in. They’ll then leave you with a price which is good for 30 days.
 
LONI Aluminum & Contracting covers the entire Greater Toronto area and some parts of Northern and Southern Ontario. If you decide to move forward with us, we’ll write a detailed agreement including all the specifications we discussed. Most projects are completed within 3 to 4 weeks of the agreement. We won’t accept final payment until you are 100% satisfied.
 
Call us at 905-463-1803 for a free quote today! For out of office hours, we can be reached at 647-833-7665 (call or text).
 
 
Check us out on Instagram! https://www.instagram.com/lonialuminum/

profile:
Aaron Ferguson’s passion has always been carpentry. It’s a craft I learned ‘on-the-job’ working for my Father’s landscaping company. The first contract was to install cabinets for a general contractor. Word soon spread about the company's work ethic, and our service offering expanded to interior trim, framing and siding. By 2005, we needed to hire full-time employees to help him deliver our services to an ever expanding list of satisfied clients. Our reputation attracted designers and builders of higher-end homes from across Toronto, the GTA and York Region.
Evergreen Carpentry now enjoys a reputation as the go-to option for contractors, builders and homeowners when they want top quality trim and siding products and workmanship. But many things remain the same as when Aaron decided to take that first job:
Work With Passion
Demonstrate Excellence in Execution Service
Safety First Always
